{"tid":1130703,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"捷克國腳撞車亡　哥爾卡、柏比斯施斯同車受傷","createTime":"2019-04-29T08:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T17:54:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0509fdd6aba0341c1fb176c0902296b059cd062e","tid":1130703,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190429/large/1556525301_8f2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190429%2Flarge%2F1556525301_8f2d.jpg&h=e9922424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n球壇再發生令人婉惜的事件。BBC、每日郵報等媒體報道，效力土超球隊阿拉尼亞的捷克國腳蘇拿爾(Josef Sural)，周日與隊友柏比斯施斯、哥爾卡等名隊友乘坐巴士由開塞利(Kayseri)返回阿拉尼亞(Alanya)時遇上車禍，他送院搶救後不治，終年28歲。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，阿拉尼亞周日出戰土超作客開塞利的賽事，他們最終憑前熱刺球員哥爾卡的入球，以1:1逼和對手。賽後7名阿拉尼亞的球員，當中包括蘇拿爾、柏比斯施斯以及哥爾卡租用了私家巴士，由開塞利返回阿拉尼亞。豈料途中遇上了車禍，蘇拿爾送院搶救後不治。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n阿拉尼亞主席Hasan Cavusoglu指出，巴士司機當時正在打瞌睡，相信就是導致車禍的原因。28歲蘇拿爾曾代表捷克出戰2016年歐國盃決賽周，司職前鋒的他一共為國家隊上陣過20次，收獲一球。"},{"pid":"e1e9914194f060378a9d2ecf658a6c54330676cc","tid":1130703,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190429/59543631\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190429%2F59543631&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9QogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=1134db15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190429%2F59543631&h=89a6de74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190429/59543631</a>"},{"pid":"4e9161954ed5328ec7eaa671c8e02bc600f1cdd9","tid":1130703,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:30:14.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"bb4ac563d61b09457f1e725eed19b699dbe3ca2d","tid":1130703,"uid":475